title: Hour 3 - NFL Recap, Rick Neuheisel
itunes:title: Hour 3 - NFL Recap, Rick Neuheisel
description:
Ross Tucker is filling in for Dan Patrick and he recaps the weekend of NFL football. Plus, he talks to former college football head coach Rick Neuheisel who thinks Ohio State is currently the best team in the country.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
